<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Wedora — Where Royal Dreams Come Alive</title>
  <link
    href="[fonts.googleapis.com](https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Cormorant+Garamond:ital,wght@0,300;0,400;0,600;1,300;1,400&family=Montserrat:wght@300;400;500;600&display=swap)"
    rel="stylesheet" />
  <link rel="stylesheet"
    href="[cdnjs.cloudflare.com](https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.5.0/css/all.min.css)" />
  <style>
    :root {
      --navy: #141c36;
      --gold: #D4AF37;
      --gold-light: #e8cc6a;
      --gold-dark: #a8891f;
      --ivory: #F5F0E8;
      --ivory-dim: #c9c2b4;
      --white: #ffffff;
      --transition: cubic-bezier(0.77, 0, 0.175, 1);
    }

    *,
    *::before,
    *::after {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      box-sizing: border-box;
    }

    html {
      scroll-behavior: smooth;
      font-size: 16px;
    }

    body {
      background-color: var(--navy);
      color: var(--ivory);
      font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif;
      overflow-x: hidden;
    }

    /* ── SCROLLBAR ── */
    ::-webkit-scrollbar {
      width: 4px;
    }

    ::-webkit-scrollbar-track {
      background: var(--navy);
    }

    ::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb {
      background: var(--gold);
      border-radius: 2px;
    }

    /* ── LOADER ── */
    #loader {
      position: fixed;
      inset: 0;
      background: var(--navy);
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      z-index: 9999;
      transition: opacity 0.8s ease, visibility 0.8s ease;
    }

    #loader.hide {
      opacity: 0;
      visibility: hidden;
    }

    .loader-logo {
      width: 100px;
      opacity: 0;
      animation: loaderFade 1s ease 0.3s forwards;
    }

    .loader-line {
      width: 0;
      height: 1px;
      background: var(--gold);
      margin-top: 24px;
      animation: loaderLine 1.2s ease 0.8s forwards;
    }

    .loader-text {
      font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
      color: var(--gold);
      letter-spacing: 6px;
      font-size: 0.75rem;
      margin-top: 16px;
      opacity: 0;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      animation: loaderFade 1s ease 1.5s forwards;
    }

    @keyframes loaderFade {
      to {
        opacity: 1;
      }
    }

    @keyframes loaderLine {
      to {
        width: 120px;
      }
    }

    /* ── NAV ── */
    nav {
      position: fixed;
      top: 0;
      left: 0;
      right: 0;
      z-index: 1000;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: space-between;
      padding: 24px 60px;
      transition: background 0.5s ease, padding 0.4s ease, backdrop-filter 0.5s ease;
    }

    nav.scrolled {
      background: rgba(20, 28, 54, 0.92);
      backdrop-filter: blur(16px);
      padding: 16px 60px;
      border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(212, 175, 55, 0.15);
    }

    .nav-logo img {
      height: 52px;
    }

    .nav-links {
      display: flex;
      gap: 40px;
      list-style: none;
    }

    .nav-links a {
      color: var(--ivory);
      text-decoration: none;
      font-size: 0.72rem;
      letter-spacing: 3px;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      font-weight: 500;
      position: relative;
      padding-bottom: 4px;
      transition: color 0.3s ease;
    }

    .nav-links a::after {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      bottom: 0;
      left: 0;
      width: 0;
      height: 1px;
      background: var(--gold);
      transition: width 0.4s var(--transition);
    }

    .nav-links a:hover {
      color: var(--gold);
    }

    .nav-links a:hover::after {
      width: 100%;
    }

    .nav-cta {
      background: transparent;
      border: 1px solid var(--gold);
      color: var(--gold);
      padding: 10px 28px;
      font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif;
      font-size: 0.7rem;
      letter-spacing: 3px;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      cursor: pointer;
      transition: all 0.4s ease;
      text-decoration: none;
    }

    .nav-cta:hover {
      background: var(--gold);
      color: var(--navy);
    }

    .hamburger {
      display: none;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 5px;
      cursor: pointer;
    }

    .hamburger span {
      width: 28px;
      height: 1px;
      background: var(--gold);
      transition: all 0.3s ease;
      display: block;
    }

    /* ── HERO ── */
    #hero {
      position: relative;
      height: 100vh;
      overflow: hidden;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
    }

    .hero-slides {
      position: absolute;
      inset: 0;
    }

    .hero-slide {
      position: absolute;
      inset: 0;
      background-size: cover;
      background-position: center;
      opacity: 0;
      transition: opacity 1.8s ease;
    }

    .hero-slide.active {
      opacity: 1;
    }

    .hero-slide::after {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      inset: 0;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg,
          rgba(20, 28, 54, 0.85) 0%,
          rgba(20, 28, 54, 0.4) 50%,
          rgba(20, 28, 54, 0.7) 100%);
    }

    .hero-slide-1 {
      background-image: url('[images.unsplash.com](https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1519741497674-611481863552?w=1920&q=80)');
    }

    .hero-slide-2 {
      background-image: url('[images.unsplash.com](https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1464366400600-7168b8af9bc3?w=1920&q=80)');
    }

    .hero-slide-3 {
      background-image: url('[images.unsplash.com](https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1511795409834-ef04bbd61622?w=1920&q=80)');
    }

    .hero-slide-4 {
      background-image: url('[images.unsplash.com](https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1520854221256-17451cc331bf?w=1920&q=80)');
    }

    .hero-content {
      position: relative;
      z-index: 2;
      text-align: center;
      padding: 0 20px;
    }

    .hero-eyebrow {
      font-size: 0.68rem;
      letter-spacing: 6px;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--gold);
      margin-bottom: 20px;
      opacity: 0;
      animation: fadeUp 1s ease 2.2s forwards;
    }

    .hero-title {
      font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
      font-size: clamp(3.5rem, 8vw, 7rem);
      font-weight: 300;
      line-height: 1.05;
      color: var(--ivory);
      margin-bottom: 24px;
      opacity: 0;
      animation: fadeUp 1s ease 2.5s forwards;
    }

    .hero-title span {
      color: var(--gold);
      font-style: italic;
    }

    .hero-sub {
      font-size: 0.78rem;
      letter-spacing: 3px;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--ivory-dim);
      margin-bottom: 48px;
      opacity: 0;
      animation: fadeUp 1s ease 2.8s forwards;
    }

    .hero-btns {
      display: flex;
      gap: 20px;
      justify-content: center;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      opacity: 0;
      animation: fadeUp 1s ease 3.1s forwards;
    }

    .btn-primary {
      background: var(--gold);
      color: var(--navy);
      padding: 16px 44px;
      font-size: 0.72rem;
      letter-spacing: 3px;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      text-decoration: none;
      font-weight: 600;
      transition: all 0.4s ease;
      border: 1px solid var(--gold);
      font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif;
    }

    .btn-primary:hover {
      background: transparent;
      color: var(--gold);
    }

    .btn-outline {
      background: transparent;
      color: var(--ivory);
      padding: 16px 44px;
      font-size: 0.72rem;
      letter-spacing: 3px;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      text-decoration: none;
      font-weight: 500;
      border: 1px solid rgba(245, 240, 232, 0.4);
      transition: all 0.4s ease;
      font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif;
    }

    .btn-outline:hover {
      border-color: var(--gold);
      color: var(--gold);
    }

    .hero-scroll {
      position: absolute;
      bottom: 40px;
      left: 50%;
      transform: translateX(-50%);
      z-index: 2;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 8px;
      opacity: 0;
      animation: fadeUp 1s ease 3.4s forwards;
    }

    .hero-scroll span {
      font-size: 0.6rem;
      letter-spacing: 4px;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--ivory-dim);
    }

    .scroll-line {
      width: 1px;
      height: 50px;
      background: linear-gradient(to bottom, var(--gold), transparent);
      animation: scrollPulse 2s ease infinite;
    }

    @keyframes scrollPulse {

      0%,
      100% {
        opacity: 1;
        transform: scaleY(1);
      }

      50% {
        opacity: 0.4;
        transform: scaleY(0.8);
      }
    }

    .hero-dots {
      position: absolute;
      bottom: 40px;
      right: 60px;
      z-index: 2;
      display: flex;
      gap: 10px;
    }

    .hero-dot {
      width: 6px;
      height: 6px;
      border-radius: 50%;
      background: rgba(245, 240, 232, 0.3);
      cursor: pointer;
      transition: all 0.4s ease;
    }

    .hero-dot.active {
      background: var(--gold);
      width: 24px;
      border-radius: 3px;
    }

    @keyframes fadeUp {
      from {
        opacity: 0;
        transform: translateY(30px);
      }

      to {
        opacity: 1;
        transform: translateY(0);
      }
    }

    /* ── MARQUEE ── */
    .marquee-section {
      border-top: 1px solid rgba(212, 175, 55, 0.2);
      border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(212, 175, 55, 0.2);
      padding: 18px 0;
      overflow: hidden;
      background: rgba(212, 175, 55, 0.04);
    }

    .marquee-track {
      display: flex;
      gap: 60px;
      width: max-content;
      animation: marquee 30s linear infinite;
    }

    .marquee-item {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 20px;
      font-size: 0.65rem;
      letter-spacing: 4px;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--ivory-dim);
      white-space: nowrap;
    }

    .marquee-item .dot {
      width: 4px;
      height: 4px;
      border-radius: 50%;
      background: var(--gold);
    }

    @keyframes marquee {
      from {
        transform: translateX(0);
      }

      to {
        transform: translateX(-50%);
      }
    }

    /* ── SECTIONS COMMON ── */
    section {
      padding: 120px 60px;
    }

    .section-label {
      font-size: 0.62rem;
      letter-spacing: 5px;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--gold);
      margin-bottom: 16px;
    }

    .section-title {
      font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
      font-size: clamp(2.4rem, 5vw, 4rem);
      font-weight: 300;
      line-height: 1.1;
      color: var(--ivory);
    }

    .section-title span {
      color: var(--gold);
      font-style: italic;
    }

    .gold-line {
      width: 60px;
      height: 1px;
      background: var(--gold);
      margin: 28px 0;
    }

    /* ── ABOUT INTRO ── */
    #about-intro {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
      gap: 100px;
      align-items: center;
    }

    .about-text p {
      font-size: 0.88rem;
      line-height: 1.95;
      color: var(--ivory-dim);
      margin-bottom: 20px;
      font-weight: 300;
    }

    .about-text p strong {
      color: var(--ivory);
      font-weight: 500;
    }

    .about-image-wrap {
      position: relative;
    }

    .about-image-wrap img {
      width: 100%;
      height: 580px;
      object-fit: cover;
      display: block;
    }

    .about-image-border {
      position: absolute;
      top: 20px;
      left: 20px;
      right: -20px;
      bottom: -20px;
      border: 1px solid rgba(212, 175, 55, 0.3);
      z-index: -1;
    }

    .about-badge {
      position: absolute;
      bottom: -30px;
      left: -30px;
      background: var(--navy);
      border: 1px solid var(--gold);
      padding: 24px 32px;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .about-badge .num {
      font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
      font-size: 3rem;
      color: var(--gold);
      line-height: 1;
    }

    .about-badge .lbl {
      font-size: 0.6rem;
      letter-spacing: 3px;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--ivory-dim);
      margin-top: 6px;
    }

    /* ── STATS ── */
    #stats {
      padding: 80px 60px;
      border-top: 1px solid rgba(212, 175, 55, 0.1);
      border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(212, 175, 55, 0.1);
      background: rgba(212, 175, 55, 0.03);
    }

    .stats-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
      gap: 20px;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .stat-item {
      padding: 20px;
    }

    .stat-num {
      font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
      font-size: 3.5rem;
      color: var(--gold);
      line-height: 1;
      font-weight: 300;
    }

    .stat-plus {
      font-size: 2rem;
      vertical-align: super;
    }

    .stat-label {
      font-size: 0.65rem;
      letter-spacing: 3px;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--ivory-dim);
      margin-top: 12px;
    }

    .stat-divider {
      width: 1px;
      background: rgba(212, 175, 55, 0.2);
      margin: auto;
    }

    /* ── SERVICES ── */
    #services {
      background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15);
    }

    .services-header {
      text-align: center;
      margin-bottom: 70px;
    }

    .services-header .gold-line {
      margin: 28px auto;
    }

    .services-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
      gap: 2px;
    }

    .service-card {
      position: relative;
      overflow: hidden;
      padding: 52px 40px;
      cursor: pointer;
      border: 1px solid rgba(212, 175, 55, 0.08);
      transition: all 0.5s var(--transition);
      background: rgba(20, 28, 54, 0.5);
    }

    .service-card::before {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      inset: 0;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(212, 175, 55, 0.08), transparent);
      opacity: 0;
      transition: opacity 0.5s ease;
    }

    .service-card:hover::before {
      opacity: 1;
    }

    .service-card:hover {
      border-color: rgba(212, 175, 55, 0.4);
      transform: translateY(-4px);
    }

    .service-icon {
      font-size: 2rem;
      color: var(--gold);
      margin-bottom: 24px;
      display: block;
      transition: transform 0.4s ease;
    }

    .service-card:hover .service-icon {
      transform: scale(1.15);
    }

    .service-num {
      position: absolute;
      top: 24px;
      right: 28px;
      font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
      font-size: 3.5rem;
      color: rgba(212, 175, 55, 0.06);
      font-weight: 300;
      line-height: 1;
    }

    .service-card h3 {
      font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
      font-size: 1.5rem;
      color: var(--ivory);
      margin-bottom: 14px;
      font-weight: 400;
    }

    .service-card p {
      font-size: 0.8rem;
      color: var(--ivory-dim);
      line-height: 1.8;
      font-weight: 300;
    }

    .service-arrow {
      margin-top: 28px;
      color: var(--gold);
      font-size: 0.75rem;
      letter-spacing: 2px;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      opacity: 0;
      transform: translateX(-10px);
      transition: all 0.4s ease;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 10px;
    }

    .service-card:hover .service-arrow {
      opacity: 1;
      transform: translateX(0);
    }

    /* ── GALLERY PREVIEW ── */
    #gallery-preview {
      padding: 120px 60px;
    }

    .gallery-header {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: flex-end;
      margin-bottom: 60px;
    }

    .gallery-header a {
      color: var(--gold);
      text-decoration: none;
      font-size: 0.7rem;
      letter-spacing: 3px;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(212, 175, 55, 0.4);
      padding-bottom: 4px;
      transition: border-color 0.3s ease;
    }

    .gallery-header a:hover {
      border-color: var(--gold);
    }

    .gallery-themes {
      display: flex;
      gap: 12px;
      margin-bottom: 40px;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
    }

    .theme-tag {
      padding: 8px 20px;
      border: 1px solid rgba(212, 175, 55, 0.25);
      font-size: 0.65rem;
      letter-spacing: 2px;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--ivory-dim);
      cursor: pointer;
      transition: all 0.3s ease;
      background: transparent;
    }

    .theme-tag:hover,
    .theme-tag.active {
      border-color: var(--gold);
      color: var(--gold);
      background: rgba(212, 175, 55, 0.06);
    }

    .gallery-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(12, 1fr);
      grid-template-rows: auto;
      gap: 8px;
    }

    .gallery-item {
      overflow: hidden;
      position: relative;
      cursor: pointer;
    }

    .gallery-item:nth-child(1) {
      grid-column: span 5;
      grid-row: span 2;
    }

    .gallery-item:nth-child(2) {
      grid-column: span 4;
    }

    .gallery-item:nth-child(3) {
      grid-column: span 3;
    }

    .gallery-item:nth-child(4) {
      grid-column: span 4;
    }

    .gallery-item:nth-child(5) {
      grid-column: span 3;
    }

    .gallery-item:nth-child(6) {
      grid-column: span 5;
    }

    .gallery-item img {
      width: 100%;
      height: 100%;
      object-fit: cover;
      min-height: 220px;
      transition: transform 0.8s var(--transition);
      display: block;
    }

    .gallery-item:hover img {
      transform: scale(1.08);
    }

    .gallery-item-overlay {
      position: absolute;
      inset: 0;
      background: linear-gradient(to top, rgba(20, 28, 54, 0.85), transparent 50%);
      opacity: 0;
      transition: opacity 0.4s ease;
      display: flex;
      align-items: flex-end;
      padding: 24px;
    }

    .gallery-item:hover .gallery-item-overlay {
      opacity: 1;
    }

    .gallery-item-label {
      font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
      font-size: 1.1rem;
      color: var(--ivory);
      font-style: italic;
    }

    /* ── VENUES ── */
    #venues {
      background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15);
    }

    .venues-header {
      text-align: center;
      margin-bottom: 70px;
    }

    .venues-header .gold-line {
      margin: 28px auto;
    }

    .venues-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
      gap: 24px;
    }

    .venue-card {
      position: relative;
      overflow: hidden;
      height: 400px;
      cursor: pointer;
    }

    .venue-card img {
      width: 100%;
      height: 100%;
      object-fit: cover;
      transition: transform 0.8s var(--transition);
    }

    .venue-card:hover img {
      transform: scale(1.08);
    }

    .venue-overlay {
      position: absolute;
      inset: 0;
      background: linear-gradient(to top, rgba(20, 28, 54, 0.92) 0%, rgba(20, 28, 54, 0.2) 60%, transparent 100%);
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      justify-content: flex-end;
      padding: 36px 32px;
    }

    .venue-tag {
      font-size: 0.6rem;
      letter-spacing: 3px;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--gold);
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }

    .venue-name {
      font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
      font-size: 1.8rem;
      color: var(--ivory);
      font-weight: 300;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
      line-height: 1.1;
    }

    .venue-desc {
      font-size: 0.75rem;
      color: var(--ivory-dim);
      line-height: 1.7;
      font-weight: 300;
      max-width: 280px;
    }

    .venue-card::before {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      inset: 0;
      border: 2px solid transparent;
      transition: border-color 0.4s ease;
      z-index: 2;
    }

    .venue-card:hover::before {
      border-color: rgba(212, 175, 55, 0.5);
    }

    /* ── TESTIMONIALS ── */
    #testimonials {
      padding: 120px 60px;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .testimonials-header .gold-line {
      margin: 28px auto;
    }

    .testimonial-slider {
      position: relative;
      max-width: 800px;
      margin: 60px auto 0;
    }

    .testimonial-slide {
      display: none;
      animation: fadeUp 0.6s ease;
    }

    .testimonial-slide.active {
      display: block;
    }

    .testimonial-quote {
      font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
      font-size: clamp(1.3rem, 3vw, 1.9rem);
      color: var(--ivory);
      line-height: 1.65;
      font-style: italic;
      font-weight: 300;
      margin-bottom: 36px;
    }

    .testimonial-quote::before {
      content: '\201C';
      color: var(--gold);
      font-size: 3rem;
      line-height: 0;
      vertical-align: -0.5rem;
      margin-right: 4px;
    }

    .testimonial-author {
      font-size: 0.7rem;
      letter-spacing: 3px;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--gold);
    }

    .testimonial-location {
      font-size: 0.65rem;
      color: var(--ivory-dim);
      margin-top: 6px;
      letter-spacing: 2px;
    }

    .testimonial-stars {
      color: var(--gold);
      margin-bottom: 16px;
      font-size: 0.8rem;
    }

    .testimonial-nav {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
      gap: 12px;
      margin-top: 48px;
    }

    .t-dot {
      width: 6px;
      height: 6px;
      border-radius: 50%;
      background: rgba(245, 240, 232, 0.2);
      cursor: pointer;
      transition: all 0.3s ease;
    }

    .t-dot.active {
      background: var(--gold);
      width: 20px;
      border-radius: 3px;
    }

    /* ── CTA BANNER ── */
    #cta-banner {
      padding: 120px 60px;
      text-align: center;
      position: relative;
      overflow: hidden;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(212, 175, 55, 0.08) 0%, rgba(20, 28, 54, 1) 50%, rgba(212, 175, 55, 0.05) 100%);
    }

    #cta-banner::before {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      top: 50%;
      left: 50%;
      transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
      width: 600px;
      height: 600px;
      border-radius: 50%;
      border: 1px solid rgba(212, 175, 55, 0.08);
    }

    #cta-banner::after {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      top: 50%;
      left: 50%;
      transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
      width: 400px;
      height: 400px;
      border-radius: 50%;
      border: 1px solid rgba(212, 175, 55, 0.1);
    }

    .cta-content {
      position: relative;
      z-index: 1;
    }

    .cta-title {
      font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
      font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 5vw, 4.5rem);
      color: var(--ivory);
      font-weight: 300;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
      line-height: 1.1;
    }

    .cta-title span {
      color: var(--gold);
      font-style: italic;
    }

    .cta-sub {
      font-size: 0.78rem;
      color: var(--ivory-dim);
      letter-spacing: 2px;
      margin-bottom: 48px;
      max-width: 480px;
      margin-left: auto;
      margin-right: auto;
      line-height: 1.8;
    }

    .cta-btns {
      display: flex;
      gap: 20px;
      justify-content: center;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
    }

    .btn-whatsapp {
      background: #25D366;
      color: white;
      padding: 16px 44px;
      font-size: 0.72rem;
      letter-spacing: 3px;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      text-decoration: none;
      font-weight: 600;
      transition: all 0.4s ease;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 10px;
      font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif;
    }

    .btn-whatsapp:hover {
      background: #1ebe5d;
      transform: translateY(-2px);
    }

    /* ── FOOTER ── */
    footer {
      background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
      border-top: 1px solid rgba(212, 175, 55, 0.15);
      padding: 80px 60px 40px;
    }

    .footer-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 2fr 1fr 1fr 1fr;
      gap: 60px;
      margin-bottom: 60px;
    }

    .footer-brand img {
      height: 64px;
      margin-bottom: 24px;
    }

    .footer-brand p {
      font-size: 0.78rem;
      color: var(--ivory-dim);
      line-height: 1.9;
      font-weight: 300;
      max-width: 280px;
    }

    .footer-col h4 {
      font-size: 0.65rem;
      letter-spacing: 3px;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--gold);
      margin-bottom: 24px;
    }

    .footer-col ul {
      list-style: none;
    }

    .footer-col ul li {
      margin-bottom: 12px;
    }

    .footer-col ul li a {
      color: var(--ivory-dim);
      text-decoration: none;
      font-size: 0.8rem;
      font-weight: 300;
      transition: color 0.3s ease;
    }

    .footer-col ul li a:hover {
      color: var(--gold);
    }

    .footer-contact-item {
      display: flex;
      gap: 14px;
      margin-bottom: 16px;
      align-items: flex-start;
    }

    .footer-contact-item i {
      color: var(--gold);
      font-size: 0.85rem;
      margin-top: 2px;
    }

    .footer-contact-item span {
      font-size: 0.78rem;
      color: var(--ivory-dim);
      font-weight: 300;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }

    .footer-social {
      display: flex;
      gap: 14px;
      margin-top: 28px;
    }

    .social-icon {
      width: 38px;
      height: 38px;
      border: 1px solid rgba(212, 175, 55, 0.3);
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      color: var(--ivory-dim);
      font-size: 0.85rem;
      transition: all 0.3s ease;
      text-decoration: none;
    }

    .social-icon:hover {
      border-color: var(--gold);
      color: var(--gold);
      background: rgba(212, 175, 55, 0.08);
    }

    .footer-bottom {
      border-top: 1px solid rgba(212, 175, 55, 0.1);
      padding-top: 32px;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: center;
    }

    .footer-bottom p {
      font-size: 0.7rem;
      color: var(--ivory-dim);
      letter-spacing: 1px;
    }

    .footer-bottom span {
      color: var(--gold);
    }

    /* ── WHATSAPP FLOAT ── */
    .whatsapp-float {
      position: fixed;
      bottom: 36px;
      right: 36px;
      z-index: 999;
      width: 56px;
      height: 56px;
      border-radius: 50%;
      background: #25D366;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      color: white;
      font-size: 1.5rem;
      text-decoration: none;
      box-shadow: 0 8px 32px rgba(37, 211, 102, 0.4);
      transition: all 0.3s ease;
      animation: pulse 2.5s ease infinite;
    }

    .whatsapp-float:hover {
      transform: scale(1.1);
      background: #1ebe5d;
    }

    @keyframes pulse {

      0%,
      100% {
        box-shadow: 0 8px 32px rgba(37, 211, 102, 0.4);
      }

      50% {
        box-shadow: 0 8px 48px rgba(37, 211, 102, 0.7);
      }
    }

    /* ── SCROLL REVEAL ── */
    .reveal {
      opacity: 0;
      transform: translateY(40px);
      transition: opacity 0.9s ease, transform 0.9s var(--transition);
    }

    .reveal.visible {
      opacity: 1;
      transform: translateY(0);
    }

    /* ── MOBILE NAV ── */
    .mobile-menu {
      display: none;
      position: fixed;
      inset: 0;
      background: rgba(20, 28, 54, 0.98);
      backdrop-filter: blur(20px);
      z-index: 998;
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      gap: 36px;
    }

    .mobile-menu.open {
      display: flex;
    }

    .mobile-menu a {
      font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
      font-size: 2.5rem;
      color: var(--ivory);
      text-decoration: none;
      font-weight: 300;
      transition: color 0.3s ease;
    }

    .mobile-menu a:hover {
      color: var(--gold);
    }

    .menu-close {
      position: absolute;
      top: 28px;
      right: 36px;
      font-size: 1.5rem;
      color: var(--gold);
      cursor: pointer;
      background: none;
      border: none;
    }

    /* ── RESPONSIVE ── */
    @media (max-width: 1024px) {
      nav {
        padding: 20px 32px;
      }

      nav.scrolled {
        padding: 14px 32px;
      }

      section {
        padding: 100px 32px;
      }

      #about-intro {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
        gap: 60px;
      }

      .about-image-wrap {
        order: -1;
      }

      .stats-grid {
        grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
      }

      .stat-divider {
        display: none;
      }

      .services-grid {
        grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
      }

      .venues-grid {
        grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
      }

      .footer-grid {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
        gap: 40px;
      }
    }

    @media (max-width: 768px) {

      .nav-links,
      .nav-cta {
        display: none;
      }

      .hamburger {
        display: flex;
      }

      section {
        padding: 80px 24px;
      }

      .hero-dots {
        right: 24px;
      }

      .gallery-grid {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
      }

      .gallery-item {
        grid-column: span 1 !important;
        grid-row: span 1 !important;
      }

      .services-grid {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      }

      .venues-grid {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      }

      .footer-grid {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      }

      .footer-bottom {
        flex-direction: column;
        gap: 12px;
        text-align: center;
      }

      .gallery-header {
        flex-direction: column;
        align-items: flex-start;
        gap: 20px;
      }

      #stats {
        padding: 60px 24px;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>

<body>

  <!-- LOADER -->
  <div id="loader">
    <img src="[i.imgur.com](https://i.imgur.com/placeholder.png)" alt="Wedora" class="loader-logo" id="loader-logo" />
    <div class="loader-line"></div>
    <p class="loader-text">Wedora — Udaipur</p>
  </div>

  <!-- WHATSAPP FLOAT -->
  <a href="[wa.me](https://wa.me/918769919003)" target="_blank" class="whatsapp-float" title="Chat on WhatsApp">
    <i class="fab fa-whatsapp"></i>
  </a>

  <!-- MOBILE MENU -->
  <div class="mobile-menu" id="mobileMenu">
    <button class="menu-close" onclick="closeMobileMenu()"><i class="fas fa-times"></i></button>
    <a href="#hero" onclick="closeMobileMenu()">Home</a>
    <a href="#about-intro" onclick="closeMobileMenu()">About</a>
    <a href="#services" onclick="closeMobileMenu()">Services</a>
    <a href="gallery.html" onclick="closeMobileMenu()">Gallery</a>
    <a href="#venues" onclick="closeMobileMenu()">Venues</a>
    <a href="#contact" onclick="closeMobileMenu()">Contact</a>
  </div>

  <!-- NAV -->
  <nav id="navbar">
    <a href="#hero" class="nav-logo">
      <img src="[i.imgur.com](https://i.imgur.com/placeholder.png)" alt="Wedora" id="nav-logo-img" />
    </a>
    <ul class="nav-links">
      <li><a href="#about-intro">About</a></li>
      <li><a href="#services">Services</a></li>
      <li><a href="gallery.html">Gallery</a></li>
      <li><a href="#venues">Venues</a></li>
      <li><a href="#testimonials">Stories</a></li>
      <li><a href="#contact">Contact</a></li>
    </ul>
    <a href="[wa.me](https://wa.me/918769919003)" class="nav-cta" target="_blank">Book Consultation</a>
    <div class="hamburger" onclick="openMobileMenu()">
      <span></span><span></span><span></span>
    </div>
  </nav>

  <!-- HERO -->
  <section id="hero">
    <div class="hero-slides">
      <div class="hero-slide hero-slide-1 active"></div>
      <div class="hero-slide hero-slide-2"></div>
      <div class="hero-slide hero-slide-3"></div>
      <div class="hero-slide hero-slide-4"></div>
    </div>
    <div class="hero-content">
      <p class="hero-eyebrow">✦ Udaipur's Premier Wedding Experience ✦</p>
      <h1 class="hero-title">Where Royal<br /><span>Dreams</span> Come Alive</h1>
      <p class="hero-sub">Weddings · Décor · Experiences · Udaipur & Beyond</p>
      <div class="hero-btns">
        <a href="#gallery-preview" class="btn-primary">Explore Our Work</a>
        <a href="[wa.me](https://wa.me/918769919003)" class="btn-outline" target="_blank">Begin Your Story</a>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="hero-scroll">
      <div class="scroll-line"></div>
      <span>Scroll</span>
    </div>
    <div class="hero-dots" id="heroDots"></div>
  </section>

  <!-- MARQUEE -->
  <div class="marquee-section">
    <div class="marquee-track" id="marqueeTrack"></div>
  </div>

  <!-- ABOUT -->
  <section id="about-intro">
    <div class="about-text reveal">
      <p class="section-label">Our Story</p>
      <h2 class="section-title">Crafting <span>Moments</span><br />That Last Forever</h2>
      <div class="gold-line"></div>
      <p>We are <strong>Wedora</strong> — Udaipur's most trusted wedding décor and experience company. From the
        shimmering lakes of Udaipur to the majestic forts of Kumbhalgarh, we transform every venue into a royal canvas
        of memory.</p>
      <p>We don't just decorate. We <strong>design complete wedding experiences</strong> — from the first flower to the
        last spotlight, from mandap to carnival, from hospitality to heartfelt moments. Every event we touch becomes a
        story worth telling.</p>
      <p>Rooted in Rajasthan's grandeur, refined by modern luxury — this is <strong>the Wedora way.</strong></p>
      <div style="margin-top: 40px;">
        <a href="[wa.me](https://wa.me/918769919003)" class="btn-primary" target="_blank">Start Planning</a>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="about-image-wrap reveal">
      <img src="[images.unsplash.com](https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1519741497674-611481863552?w=800&q=80)"
        alt="Wedora Wedding Décor" />
      <div class="about-image-border"></div>
      <div class="about-badge">
        <div class="num">200<span style="font-size:1.5rem">+</span></div>
        <div class="lbl">Events Crafted</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- STATS -->
  <div id="stats">
    <div class="stats-grid">
      <div class="stat-item reveal">
        <div class="stat-num"><span class="counter" data-target="200">0</span><span class="stat-plus">+</span></div>
        <div class="stat-label">Events Crafted</div>
      </div>
      <div class="stat-divider"></div>
      <div class="stat-item reveal">
        <div class="stat-num"><span class="counter" data-target="50">0</span><span class="stat-plus">+</span></div>
        <div class="stat-label">Trusted Vendors</div>
      </div>
      <div class="stat-divider"></div>
      <div class="stat-item reveal">
        <div class="stat-num"><span class="counter" data-target="15">0</span><span class="stat-plus">+</span></div>
        <div class="stat-label">Venues Served</div>
      </div>
      <div class="stat-divider"></div>
      <div class="stat-item reveal">
        <div class="stat-num"><span class="counter" data-target="100">0</span><span class="stat-plus">%</span></div>
        <div class="stat-label">Happy Families</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- SERVICES -->
  <section id="services">
    <div class="services-header reveal">
      <p class="section-label">What We Do</p>
      <h2 class="section-title">Complete Wedding <span>Experiences</span></h2>
      <div class="gold-line"></div>
    </div>
    <div class="services-grid">
      <div class="service-card reveal">
        <span class="service-num">01</span>
        <i class="fas fa-spa service-icon"></i>
        <h3>Floral & Décor</h3>
        <p>Lush florals, intricate mandap setups, and bespoke décor that transforms any venue into a royal dreamscape.
        </p>
        <div class="service-arrow">Explore <i class="fas fa-arrow-right"></i></div>
      </div>
      <div class="service-card reveal">
        <span class="service-num">02</span>
        <i class="fas fa-music service-icon"></i>
        <h3>Stage, Sound & Lighting</h3>
        <p>Dramatic stage designs, professional sound engineering, and mood lighting that sets the perfect ambiance.</p>
        <div class="service-arrow">Explore <i class="fas fa-arrow-right"></i></div>
      </div>
      <div class="service-card reveal">
        <span class="service-num">03</span>
        <i class="fas fa-concierge-bell service-icon"></i>
        <h3>Hospitality & Venue</h3>
        <p>Seamless guest management, luxury venue coordination, and hospitality that makes every guest feel royal.</p>
        <div class="service-arrow">Explore <i class="fas fa-arrow-right"></i></div>
      </div>
      <div class="service-card reveal">
        <span class="service-num">04</span>
        <i class="fas fa-magic service-icon"></i>
        <h3>Theme Management</h3>
        <p>From royal Rajasthani to modern minimal — we conceptualize and execute immersive themes end to end.</p>
        <div class="service-arrow">Explore <i class="fas fa-arrow-right"></i></div>
      </div>
      <div class="service-card reveal">
        <span class="service-num">05</span>
        <i class="fas fa-ferris-wheel service-icon"></i>
        <h3>Carnival & Entertainment</h3>
        <p>Interactive carnival activities, live performances, and entertainment setups that delight guests of all ages.
        </p>
        <div class="service-arrow">Explore <i class="fas fa-arrow-right"></i></div>
      </div>
      <div class="service-card reveal">
        <span class="service-num">06</span>
        <i class="fas fa-handshake service-icon"></i>
        <h3>Vendor Coordination</h3>
        <p>A curated network of photographers, caterers, makeup artists, and more — all managed under one roof.</p>
        <div class="service-arrow">Explore <i class="fas fa-arrow-right"></i></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- GALLERY PREVIEW -->
  <section id="gallery-preview">
    <div class="gallery-header reveal">
      <div>
        <p class="section-label">Our Portfolio</p>
        <h2 class="section-title">Every Event, <span>A Masterpiece</span></h2>
      </div>
      <a href="gallery.html">View Full Gallery</a>
    </div>
    <div class="gallery-themes reveal">
      <button class="theme-tag active" onclick="filterGallery(this, 'all')">All</button>
      <button class="theme-tag" onclick="filterGallery(this, 'royal')">Royal Rajasthani</button>
      <button class="theme-tag" onclick="filterGallery(this, 'luxe')">Black & Gold Luxe</button>
      <button class="theme-tag" onclick="filterGallery(this, 'floral')">Floral Wonderland</button>
      <button class="theme-tag" onclick="filterGallery(this, 'garden')">Garden & Boho</button>
      <button class="theme-tag" onclick="filterGallery(this, 'destination')">Destination</button>
    </div>
    <div class="gallery-grid reveal" id="galleryGrid">
      <div class="gallery-item" data-theme="royal">
        <img src="[images.unsplash.com](https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1519741497674-611481863552?w=800&q=80)"
          alt="Royal Wedding" />
        <div class="gallery-item-overlay"><span class="gallery-item-label">Royal Rajasthani</span></div>
      </div>
      <div class="gallery-item" data-theme="floral">
        <img src="[images.unsplash.com](https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1464366400600-7168b8af9bc3?w=600&q=80)"
          alt="Floral Décor" />
        <div class="gallery-item-overlay"><span class="gallery-item-label">Floral Wonderland</span></div>
      </div>
      <div class="gallery-item" data-theme="luxe">
        <img src="[images.unsplash.com](https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1511795409834-ef04bbd61622?w=600&q=80)"
          alt="Luxe Wedding" />
        <div class="gallery-item-overlay"><span class="gallery-item-label">Black & Gold Luxe</span></div>
      </div>
      <div class="gallery-item" data-theme="garden">
        <img src="[images.unsplash.com](https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1520854221256-17451cc331bf?w=600&q=80)"
          alt="Garden Wedding" />
        <div class="gallery-item-overlay"><span class="gallery-item-label">Garden & Boho</span></div>
      </div>
      <div class="gallery-item" data-theme="destination">
        <img src="[images.unsplash.com](https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1583939003579-730e3918a45a?w=600&q=80)"
          alt="Destination Wedding" />
        <div class="gallery-item-overlay"><span class="gallery-item-label">Destination — Udaipur</span></div>
      </div>
      <div class="gallery-item" data-theme="royal">
        <img src="[images.unsplash.com](https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1469371670807-013ccf25f16a?w=800&q=80)"
          alt="Royal Décor" />
        <div class="gallery-item-overlay"><span class="gallery-item-label">Royal Mandap</span></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- VENUES -->
  <section id="venues">
    <div class="venues-header reveal">
      <p class="section-label">Where We Create Magic</p>
      <h2 class="section-title">Iconic <span>Venues</span> We Serve</h2>
      <div class="gold-line"></div>
    </div>
    <div class="venues-grid">
      <div class="venue-card reveal">
        <img src="[images.unsplash.com](https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1477587458883-47145ed94245?w=800&q=80)"
          alt="Udaipur" />
        <div class="venue-overlay">
          <p class="venue-tag">✦ City of Lakes</p>
          <h3 class="venue-name">Udaipur</h3>
          <p class="venue-desc">Palace hotels, lakeside venues, and heritage havelis — the jewel of destination
            weddings.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="venue-card reveal">
        <img src="[images.unsplash.com](https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1524492412937-b28074a5d7da?w=800&q=80)"
          alt="Kumbhalgarh" />
        <div class="venue-overlay">
          <p class="venue-tag">✦ The Great Wall of India</p>
          <h3 class="venue-name">Kumbhalgarh</h3>
          <p class="venue-desc">Fort-side ceremonies and royal landscapes that transport your wedding to another era.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="venue-card reveal">
        <img src="[images.unsplash.com](https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1562602833-0f4ab2fc46e5?w=800&q=80)"
          alt="Rajasthan" />
        <div class="venue-overlay">
          <p class="venue-tag">✦ Across Rajasthan</p>
          <h3 class="venue-name">& Beyond</h3>
          <p class="venue-desc">Chittorgarh, Ranakpur, Nathdwara — we travel wherever your dream wedding takes us.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- TESTIMONIALS -->
  <section id="testimonials">
    <div class="testimonials-header reveal">
      <p class="section-label">Love Stories</p>
      <h2 class="section-title">What Couples <span>Say</span></h2>
      <div class="gold-line"></div>
    </div>
    <div class="testimonial-slider">
      <div class="testimonial-slide active">
        <div class="testimonial-stars">★★★★★</div>
        <p class="testimonial-quote">Wedora turned our dream into reality. Every corner of the venue was pure magic —
          the florals, the lighting, the stage. Our guests couldn't stop talking about it for weeks.</p>
        <p class="testimonial-author">Priya & Arjun Sharma</p>
        <p class="testimonial-location">Lake Pichola, Udaipur</p>
      </div>
      <div class="testimonial-slide">
        <div class="testimonial-stars">★★★★★</div>
        <p class="testimonial-quote">From vendor coordination to the carnival activities, Wedora handled everything
          flawlessly. We didn't have to worry about a single thing on our wedding day.</p>
